claim.claim-text:
The sensor means or module according to claim 8 or 9,

characterized by at least one of
- a specifically increased bridge voltage (Vin) of the Wheatstone bridge circuit (55), particularly an excitation voltage, more particularly being in a range of about 5 V to about 12 V;
- a specifically increased gauge factor of the strain gauge (49), the gauge factor preferably being greater than 2 and more preferably within a range of about 5 to about 16;
- a low noise amplifier and/or a rail to rail amplifier and/or a high gain instrumentation amplifier(57).
